Package: methylXprs
Title: Associates DNA Methylation with Matched gene Expression
Version: 0.99.4
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ian",
           family = "Loveless",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "ilovele1@hfhs.org")
Description: Method to impute gene expression from DNA methylation in cancer.
    Imputed expression can be used to perform a mechanistic gene-based EWAS.
    Functionality is also provided to associate DNA methylation with gene 
    expression in a multivariate environment on one's own data. 
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
